<DocsPageSubtitle>
    5. Registrations
</DocsPageSubtitle>

<DocsPageParagraph>
    Depending on the hosting model of your Blazor project you only need to apply either step <Strong>5.a</Strong> or <Strong>5.b</Strong>.
    You should not include both of them as that is generally not supported.
</DocsPageParagraph>

<DocsPageParagraph>
